snippet.title: Valley Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming summer 2016 - www.valleythegame.com

We are proud to announce our newest videogame - Valley. In the game, players will explore the vast and beautiful world of Valley using the power of the L.E.A.F. SUIT: a fierce exoskeleton that grants exceptional speed and agility along with the phenomenal ability to manipulate the life and death of all living things.
